CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 27, 2008

[Cite as 03127/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-1397.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-1863. Middleburg Hts. v. Quinones.

Cuyahoga App. No. 88242, 2007-Ohio-3643. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of the motion of appellant and amici curiae to supplement the record,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
